35) | Context          | NGE/PGE/NSE/PSE for values | NGE/PGE/NSE/PSE for contribution |  VIMP Concept
| -------------------- | -------------------------- | -------------------------------- |
| **Next Greater**     | peek `<`  curr             | peek `<`  curr                   |
| **Previous Greater** | peek `<=` curr             | peek `<`  curr                   |
| **Next Smaller**     | peek `>`  curr             | peek `>=` curr                   |                  
| **Previous Smaller** | peek `>=` curr             | peek `>=` curr                   |               

